37.000Z","msg":"佢成日cap 張圖都唔係出波個下，停遲左<br />\n<br />\n呢樣咁簡單都做咩好仲講咩垂直<br />\n<br />\n其實應該係造波，唔係咁明顯錯誤都搞唔掂<br />\n<br />\n成日就係差個個小小錯誤就冇越比佢做到越<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714abf7be9f1a3df18e15896b71c75fc75ea91ec","tid":2328951,"uid":234945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T16:56:56.000Z","msg":"喺邊線裝部相機，好似100米賽咁不斷水平追住個波跑？"},{"pid":"50e7beba5e66c190d76036bddfb760137949e0a0","tid":2328951,"uid":312758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T17:04:00.000Z","msg":"其實攞無人機跟越位線已經搞掂<br />\n<br />\n大把方法，但就係唔做，吹咩？"},{"pid":"6360757d556b3f49e6530364bfde6b72be84ad64","tid":2328951,"uid":45591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T18:38:31.000Z","msg":"平時睇西甲都間唔中見到個攻勢360度replay比你睇<br />\n但英超就畫線仲要斜既"},{"pid":"441229a4b8e9cb67b1597914620996f32ed0012a","tid":2328951,"uid":49859,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"38018c991bbc3460f706cf3a7961fd649fa981d8","tid":2328951,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T02:22:21.000Z","msg":"佢打斜劃線 條線都唔係同球場D線平行<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T19:15:32.000Z","msg":"屌你有冇讀過書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日見人屌話唔係畫垂直線係斜線<br />\n連登/FB仲一堆人屌咩同底線/禁區界唔平行<br />\n鏡頭平面影個立體嘅球場點樣唔同距離拉平行線呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知唔知咩叫透視，近大遠小呀<br />\n誇張啲用廣角鏡影落去底線同中線都變到八字型唔平行啦<br />\n唔通個足球場又係梯型呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用任何單鏡頭角度影落去，球場上任何平行線影出黎都一定唔會平行係好撚正常嘅事<br />\n問題根本唔關佢畫咩線事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算佢真係做到學上面講有兩邊高速Cam跟住你都一樣可以質疑兩支Cam交線同底線係咪平行<br />\n關於條線我覺得你只能信<br />\n衣家問題係如果已經有片睇，Check越位個精確度要拿捏去到邊<br />\n學上面話齋，拎邊個Frame出黎計影響仲大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83363b442de9b63f74c992998b48894f29b887eb","tid":2328951,"uid":170772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5dc7820d66c1ed90c4cc9e479fe4efe2369c9a1","tid":2328951,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b93efefb1683b0cd18f506d1e6da8140dba92665","tid":2328951,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:51:22.000Z","msg":"球鞋同波裝感應器？<br />\n計傳波落腳果下，check 越位條友係咪過左防守球員"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T15:04:03.000Z","msg":"應該幾難設計 咁激烈既運動重要放係隻鞋到<br />\n可能手臂整隻手環易d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T19:25:43.000Z","msg":"你狗？手環點detect腳觸球嗰下"},{"pid":"074e0717b2c9b2d139fd29d40318d89bf37f6ace","tid":2328951,"uid":170772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"714abf7be9f1a3df18e15896b71c75fc75ea91ec","tid":2328951,"uid":234945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T16:56:56.000Z","msg":"喺邊線裝部相機，好似100米賽咁不斷水平追住個波跑？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T19:26:49.000Z","msg":"追個波有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}